title: 5 Teams Already Eyeing 2020, Week 1 QB Grades with Brady Quinn (Football 9/11)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and Ryan Wilson to take a look back at Week 1 and ahead towards Week 2. Brady delivers his 5 teams that are already looking ahead to 2020 (2:00), a list that surprisingly includes the Indianapolis Colts (5:00). The guys then cover the most concerning Week 1 injury (11:00) and follow that by assessing grades to Kyler Murray (20:00), Carson Wentz and Marcus Mariota. Next, it's time to pick apart Pete Prisco's weekly Power Rankings (34:00) and finally, which 0-1 team needs a win the most this week (48:00)?
